string.name: wireless_projection_statement
string.value: [TS_1011246]_This service requires the Device connection permission. It uses WLAN and Bluetooth and will record device audio and onscreen content. By turning this on, you agree to these terms and the %s.

string.name: far_field_communication_service_privacy
string.value: [TS_1082162]_Statement About Far-Field Communication Services and Privacy

string.name: collaboration_recommend_service_switch_msg
string.value: [TS_1083994]_This service suggests ways to collaborate with your other devices when they are nearby. To do this, it requires an Internet connection, needs to use Bluetooth and WLAN, and will exchange data with other devices via far-field communication. For more details about how your personal information is processed, refer to the %s. By turning this on, you agree to these terms.

string.name: wireless_entry_guide_message
string.value: [TS_1122335]_Simply tap ScreenCast in the Control Panel to search for nearby devices.
